The one veld fire is burning high up on the mountain slopes, while a second is burning at Palmiet Bridge. JOHANNESBURG Firefighters in the Overberg are battling two fires in Grabouw.The one veld fire is burning high up on the mountain slopes, while a second is burning at Palmiet Bridge.The Overberg fire service s Reinard Geldenhuys says: The other one of concern is near the Palmiet Bridge, near the N2, that is causing smoke and traffic problems. That is being worked by the fire team and is almost under control. We just ask people to be careful around that area. 